&reftitle.description;

 public intSimpleXMLElement::count




 Diese Methode z채hlt die Anzahl der Kinder eines Elements.

&reftitle.examples;
Z채hlen der Kinder
<?php $xml = <<<EOF <people> <person name="Person 1"> <child/> <child/> <child/> </person> <person name="Person 2"> <child/> <child/> <child/> <child/> <child/> </person> </people> EOF;
